## Limitations

This report is based on available data and articles up to April 2025. The analysis is limited by the scope of the sources reviewed and the inherent uncertainties in economic forecasting. Additionally, the dynamic nature of global markets means that new developments could alter the current understanding of the dollar's weakening. Further research and continuous monitoring of economic indicators are recommended for a more comprehensive analysis.